Invocation Name: west l. a. guide
des:
The West La guide is meant to help users find local restaurants and shops that serve anything from coffee to tacos. 
Start by saying "Alexa open west L.A. guide then ask questions like "where are some lunch spots around me" or simply say "coffee" for a tasty breakfast spot near by.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
